<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dietrich Hofer zu Sünching, Verweser Niederbayerns</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Maurer, Diener der Stadt, wegen Kaspar Hertenberger an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_76" id="36v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_76_line_1574331901514_985"> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Dyetrich Hofer cʒu <expan>Sinching<ex>en</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">oder </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l26">
<del rend="strikethrough">wer 
<add><ab facs="#facs_76_line_1574331923701_1000">cʒu der cʒeıt </ab></add> des edeln wolgeporen h<ex>er</ex>ren Graf </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l27">
<del rend="strikethrough">Ecʒels von Ortemberg / vicʒtums in </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l28">
<del rend="strikethrough">Nẏdern Beyern </del> / vervveſer iſt </ab></del>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l29"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Dyetrıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hofer cʒu <expan>Sinching<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_76_r2l30">vervveſer des lands in Nẏdern Bayern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_76_r2l31">Lıeber her Dyetrıch Als Jr vns nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt </ab><ab facs="#facs_76_r2l32">von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> dyetrich hof </del> / Caſpar hertembergers wegen / </ab><ab facs="#facs_76_r2l33">darümb <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> wır cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> hanſen Mawrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_76_r2l34">diener mit ew / dauon cʒu reden / vnd <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_76_r2l35">mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒe / vvaʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıener darümb cʒu <expan>diſe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_76_r2l36">mal etc . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vȷ̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex>ıs</expan> <expan>Bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_76" id="36v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Dyetrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Hofer czu
                            <expan>Sinching<ex>en</ex></expan>, verweser des lands in Nydern Bayern
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Dyetrich, als ir uns nehst
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Caspar Hertembergers wegen, darümb
                                <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> wir czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> Hansen Mawrer,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit ew davon czu reden. Und
                                <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisze,
                        waz der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener darümb czu
                            <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan> mal etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex>is</expan>
<expan>bap<ex>tis</ex>
<hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
